title: Scent.of.the.night
description:
The smell/scent of the night by Andrea Camilleri.


A financier-con artist has disappeared, as has a large amount of money that a lot of retirees invested with him. An investigation had been undertaken but it seems to have gone nowhere. 
Everyone seems to be resigned to the idea that the Mafia have dealt with a problem. 

It's not until one elderly local man finds the news that his money has gone too much for him, and starts waving a gun around, that Inspector Montalbano's interest is sparked.


What is interesting is the grumpy Montalbano, and the atmosphere of Sicily the book evokes.


Bit rate 32 kbps.


I'll be seeding in 3 hours from now
